{"tid":2016132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小米老闆被抓包用iPhone！ 粉絲崩潰引爆網路","createTime":"2020-05-14T07:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T14:10:10.000Z","uid":39470,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27e05d9dffa0fca56b094b978c2270cce20831d4","tid":2016132,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"2020年5月14日<br />\n<br />\n<strong>小米老闆被抓包用iPhone！ 粉絲崩潰引爆網路</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/3165441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F3165441&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=8958616e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F3165441&h=3d527445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/3165441</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕小米科技創始人、董事長兼執行長雷軍被視為小米手機的最大代言人，最近卻被發現使用蘋果公司的iPhone手機在微博發文，讓許多小米粉絲「米粉」不滿，消息在網路上瘋傳，成為中國網路的熱門話題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/05/14/phpHbwk37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F05%2F14%2FphpHbwk37.jpg&h=fbb54b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國一名網友日前在微博上鼓勵小米，雷軍回覆2個笑臉以示感謝，但卻被網友發現這個發文「來自 iPhone 客戶端」，這項舉動隨即引發「米粉」不滿。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n中國一名網友日前在微博上鼓勵小米，雷軍回覆2個笑臉以示感謝，但卻被網友發現這個發文「來自 iPhone 客戶端」，這項舉動隨即引發「米粉」不滿，諷刺雷軍不用自家的旗艦機，難道是看不上自家的產品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2020/05/14/phpfnrFN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F05%2F14%2FphpfnrFN5.jpg&h=3f1a4641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小米合夥人潘九堂發文說，如果哪家手機公司老闆或產品經理宣稱不試用體驗蘋果、三星產品，要不是虛偽，不然就是不關心產品或遠離一線，科技創新與進步又不是大家關在屋子或寺廟裡各自頓悟。（圖擷取自微博）<br />\n<br />\n當初被雷軍回覆的網友非常難過，他自稱是8年「米粉」，使用過小米2、小米1S、小米4、小米6、小米MIX2S、紅米Note 、紅米K20 Pro等小米生產的手機，並說雷軍已經將他的留言刪除。<br />\n<br />\n對此，小米合夥人潘九堂發文說，如果哪家手機公司老闆或產品經理宣稱不試用體驗蘋果、三星產品，要不是虛偽，不然就是不關心產品或遠離一線，科技創新與進步又不是大家關在屋子或寺廟裡各自頓悟。"},{"pid":"b77054f948da55a858c73ea0d19d81df24b42218","tid":2016132,"uid":76063,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:39:39.000Z","msg":"佢唔親身用iphone 點抄哂D野落屌米到"},{"pid":"08c3f11e0e89e86372456dccb112c0411a163d07","tid":2016132,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"屌米狗，只有比人當狗撚的份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec56dc1c16192fe314e45d4cbbacbb11bbbb8ac","tid":2016132,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"建議樓主，開個post係手機台，會多人傾啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72f8872e4d968b4e0b096de84ae5d6c2fed5390","tid":2016132,"uid":274722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"支那種係咁<br />\n日鳩日叫你愛國要感激習大大既都係揸美國綠卡住外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04fa56a94537208e807ece81c2ed3b5d718643ab","tid":2016132,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae198e65ec188d3d26355564730121309d55a86","tid":2016132,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4ec56dc1c16192fe314e45d4cbbacbb11bbbb8ac","tid":2016132,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"建議樓主，開個post係手機台，會多人傾啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"手殘出錯台<img src=\"/ass